    <Placemark>
        <name>How to Remove a President</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>How to Remove a President</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 11:00 PM UTC - 1:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>College of Complexes (Dapper Restaurant)<br>2901 W Addison St<br>Chicago, IL 60618</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> RefuseFascism.org</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>### College of Complexes 
**Dapper Restaurant
2901 W. Addison (between California/Sacramento), Chicago, free parking. Tuition $3.00 and food/drink purchase**

RSVP for Zoom link alternative

[Paul Street](https://substack.com/@paulstreet), author, journalist and member of the national board of Refuse Fascism, will speak at the College of Complexes on &quot;How to Remove a President.&quot;

That&apos;s the urgent challenge facing all of us who refuse to turn away from the growing list of crimes committed and underway by this Trump regime. To name a few: threats to attack Iran, increasing the deadly &quot;defense budget&quot; by another 50%, and repealing the 2009 Endangerment finding that allowed the EPA to restrict greenhouse gases polluting our air. 
 
The courage and tenacity of the people of Minneapolis in protesting ICE crimes is inspiring. ICE is the battering ram of a much broader agenda to remake society in a much more repressive, destructive direction. That&apos;s why we all must unite to demand: the Trump fascist regime must go NOW! 
 
[The People&apos;s Indictment](https://refusefascism.org/featured-news/peoples-indictment/) delivered to the White House in December exposes the utter illegitimacy of Trump and his whole gang. But how can the people actually remove such a dangerous fascist? That&apos;s what Paul Street will explain at the College of Complexes meeting this Saturday. Read more [here](https://refusefascism.org/uncategorized/frequently-asked-questions/) and join the conversation Saturday, in person or online. There&apos;s no time to waste if we&apos;re going to stop these lunatics before fascism is completely consolidated.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/906255/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
