    <Placemark>
        <name>Canvassing in Lincoln Square</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Canvassing in Lincoln Square</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, February 20, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Lincoln Square<br><br>Chicago, IL 60625</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Matt Conroy For Congress</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Are you frustrated with the lack of leadership within the Democratic Party? Are you sick of elected officials that serve themselves and their corporate donors before serving you? We&apos;re fighting for a better future that provides you with universal healthcare, affordable housing for everyone, abolishing and prosecuting ICE, and ending the genocide in Gaza.

Is that the future you want? If so, then join us Friday, February 20th for a canvass in Lincoln Square. 

What you need to bring:

🧤 Hats, Gloves &amp; a Coat (or whatever will keep you warm!)

📲 Your Cell Phone (Don&apos;t Forget to Charge It!!!)

👟 Comfortable shoes

👯 Bring A Friend!

Official meet up spot will be sent to you upon registering! We will train you up on what you need to do, as well as provide all of the handouts and door hangers you&apos;ll need!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/904301/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
