    <Placemark>
        <name>South Suburban Relentless</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>South Suburban Relentless</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>14700 LaGrange Rd<br>Orland Park, IL 60462</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This a local Indivisible event!

On February 21, 1958 the Peace sign ☮️was designed by Gerald Holtom. Sixty-eight years later, South Suburban Relentless will hold it&apos;s Peaceful Protest on 2/21/26. 14700 LaGrange Road. Orland Park, IL. from 11am until 1pm. Some of the rules need to be gone over. if you invite friends please share the rules with them. NO engagement with counter protesters. Turn way from them and face the street. If they ask you to show them your sign, don&apos;t. Monitors are always on site. If you  have a whistle, use it once or twice to get a Monitors attention. Keep at least 2 feet away from the curb. Do not go into the median to take pictures. Please be civil with your signs. We want to respect the community and there are children everywhere. This is not censorship, it is our approach to having our voices heard. The counter protesters signs are vulgar and filled with profanity. You do not want to be mistaken for one of them. We have a huge Sign/Flag Library that we welcome you to borrow from. Verda&apos;s Food Drive will be open. We sincerely appreciate your generosity. If you are struggling with food insecurity, see one of our Monitors and we&apos;ll sort that out. Ice Out! He&apos;s in the epstein files! When injustice becomes law, RESISTANCE becomes DUTY!

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/901201/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
