    <Placemark>
        <name>Whistle Kit/Senate Debate Watch Party - Elk Grove Village, Illinois</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Whistle Kit/Senate Debate Watch Party - Elk Grove Village, Illinois</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, February 20, 2026 at 12:30 AM UTC - 2:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Real Time Sports Bar &amp; Grill<br>1120 W Devon Ave<br>Elk Grove Village, IL 60007</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible Elk Grove Township</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>**Join Indivisible Elk Grove Township in blowing the whistle on ICE!**

Whistle Kit making parties are a community safety practice rooted in resistance movements to help alert neighbors during immigration raids.

In moments like these, we’re reminded that protection is not just a policy, it’s a community responsibility.

Make new friends, watch the U.S. Senate debate, and discuss local and national issues, all while saving democracy by making Whistle Kits **TOGETHER**!

We will provide all you&apos;ll need, including zines, Know Your Rights cards, and whistle kit supplies! We ask that you take kits home with you to distribute to local business, neighbors, and anyone who is in this fight with us. Bring yourself, and perhaps a few friends! 

Real Time Sports Bar &amp; Grill is graciously allowing us to use their location, so  we ask that you please purchase food and beverages while you&apos;re here. Everyone will receive their own individual tab. Please tip your server!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/891616/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
