        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Thursday Phone Bank with Melissa Bean For Congress</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, February 19, 2026 at 11:00 PM UTC - 2:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>1750 E Golf Rd<br>Schaumburg, IL 60173</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Melissa Bean for Congress</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Come join us at our campaign office to phone bank for Melissa Bean for Congress! 

The Bean is Back! Melissa Bean is a three term former Congresswoman, who has made strives for our community. Melissa is ready to get back in office and continue to uplift our community and tackle pressing issues facing the US, such as unmasking ICE, protecting womens rights, empowering young americans, making healthcare and housing affordable, and much more. 

Together we will reach out to engage voters and inform them about Melissa Beans plans to represent the IL 08th district. 

Organizers will be available to train all volunteers and answer any questions throughout this event.</p>
