        <name>Whistle Kit Making for No Kings 3!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Whistle Kit Making for No Kings 3!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 6:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>TBD<br><br>Gurnee, IL 60031</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> NE Lake County IL Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>**Join NE Lake County Indivisible Outreach Team for whistle kit making!**

Whistle kits are an effective way to make sure our friends &amp; neighbors know their rights, and can alert others when ICE is in the area. We use whistle kits in all our residential and business canvassing, and we&apos;re looking to put together 2,000 kits to have on March 28th for No Kings 3!

While our outreach team has been hard at work, we need some additional support for this massive effort. This is also a good chance to come spend time with like-minded people, and hear about all the other good work the outreach team does if you have not been to an event before. We will provide all training and supplies, so just bring yourself (and a friend or two)!

**Keep a lookout for a Mobilize update providing meetup details about 2 days before the event itself, as we are currently relocating depending on crowd size.**

*This event is planned by the Outreach Team of NE Lake County Indivisible.*

**ABOUT NE LAKE COUNTY INDIVISIBLE:**

NE Lake County IL Indivisible is a nonpartisan grassroots organization founded in 2025 in defense of democracy. We are Lake County residents working together to protect elections and neighbors. We aim to support targeted populations and take action on a local and national level to push back against authoritarianism. We welcome everyone, whether you voted this way or that way, or didn&apos;t vote at all in 2024.

More about us can be found here:

https://nelakecounty-indivisible.org/ https://linktr.ee/nelakecountyindivisible</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/904607/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
