        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Signs of Solidarity - Business Canvass Training</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, February 19, 2026 at 3:30 PM UTC - 4:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Chapbook Cafe at Schuler Books<br>2660 28th St SE suite G<br>Grand Rapids, MI 49512</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> For Our Future Michigan</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join For Our Future in supporting Indivisible’s Signs of Solidarity campaign, standing with our immigrant neighbors against ICE.

Come together with others to receive materials, education, and training on canvassing local businesses to post signage in solidarity with the immigrant community. We’ll talk about what businesses we can focus on and how to best advance the efforts of this initiative together.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/845438/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
