        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Meet Your Candidates: A Forum for All Voters</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, February 26, 2026 at 11:00 PM UTC - 2:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Barry Expo Center<br>1350 M-37 Hwy<br>Hastings, MI 49058</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This is a local Indivisible event!

This event offers our community the opportunity to meet and interact with statewide candidates and hear them answer questions on key issues, including healthcare, immigration/ICE, the economy, foreign policy, elections and voting. All candidates were invited, and the following have confirmed. Candidates for: Governor - Anthony Hudson (R) and Sheriff Chris Swanson (D). Senate - Abdul El-Sayed (D) and Rachel Howard (D). Attorney General - Eli Savit (D). Secretary of State - Suzanna Shkreli (D). 
District 2 Representative - Ben Ambrose (D), Jamie Hill (D) and Clyde Welford (D). 

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
