<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Sauk County Youth Resistance</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Hello, Sauk County Youth Resistance is very proud to bring you its third rally, We the People Resist III. Like our previous two events, this protest condemns the countless unlawful and harmful actions of the Trump Administration, as well as the escalated ICE brutality. We meet at Meyer Oak Grove Park in Sauk City from 2 PM to 4PM. You are highly encouraged to bring a non-perishable food item for donation for local aid. We hope to see you there!</p>
