    <Placemark>
        <name>Legal &amp; Effective Immigration Enforcement</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Legal &amp; Effective Immigration Enforcement</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>South State Street &amp; Perry Avenue<br>Big Rapids, MI 49307</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This a local Indivisible event.

Enough is enough!  We have all witnessed the incredible cruelty of ICE and the Border Patrol and it is time to reform both agencies in order to stop the violation of our due rights, whether as US citizens or those here without documentation.  It is time to stop the racial profiling. It is time to reclaim the Fourth Amendment and stop the illegal entry of private homes.  It is time to stop the pepper spray and the rubber bullets and the gang tackles.  It is time to stop the outright murder of people on the streets, and it is time to stop the deaths in their concentration camps.   It&apos;s time to remind these agencies that we have a right to assemble peacefully and that we have a right to free speech.  

Please be aware that we have been experiencing some serious winter weather here, and the footing may be uncertain.  The sidewalks are usually cleared but may be icy and/or snow packed.  Please dress accordingly for the weather as there is no shelter.  There&apos;s plenty of parking and it&apos;s fairly level ground, but there are no public bathrooms.

We respectfully request that you refrain from using profanity on your signs, as this is a small town and many families with children will drive by.

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.  Weapons of any kind, including those legally permitted, should not be brought to events.*</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/894381/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
