        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Springfield - Door Knocking for Dylan Blaha: 2/22-3/1</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, February 25, 2026 at 10:00 PM UTC - 12:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Oh Icee<br>1501 Wabash Ave ste e<br>Springfield, IL 62704</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Dylan Blaha for Congress</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>## Join fellow campaign volunteers for a round of Door Knocking in Springfield. 

### Attendees will drive/walk in groups to knock on doors and let people know about Dylan&apos;s grassroots, progressive campaign. Door knocking is one of the most impactful ways to spread the word about Dylan, and it does not require any experience! 

