        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Ann Arbor ICE OUT Protest - 4 locations</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 5:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>101 N Main St<br>Ann Arbor, MI 48104</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Ann Arbor ICE OUT</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Every SATURDAY now we show up. 11am-12:30pm. ICE OUT NOW!

Great turnout on Jan. 31:  600+ people,  Let&apos;s increase that each week.

Come for whatever amount of time you can handle. It will still be frigid on Feb. 7, put warmers in your mittens and boots.

Four major intersections in Ann Arbor:

* Plymouth &amp; Green (Jeff)

* Jackson &amp; Maple (Corky)

* Stadium &amp; Main (Georgina)

* Washtenaw &amp; Huron Parkway (Gordon)

If it will be too cold, a car caravan/procession will drive around town. Be at the old Cinema 16 parking lot on Jackson Rd. BY 11 a.m.

PS: There&apos;s also a long time protest on Jackson Rd. at the Tesla dealership on Saturdays from 11 to 1.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/891978/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
