        <name>Tell Commissioners &quot;ICE out of Oakland County!&quot;</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Tell Commissioners &quot;ICE out of Oakland County!&quot;</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Monday, February 16, 2026 at 5:00 AM UTC - 4:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> NE Oakland Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Sign up and we&apos;ll send you templates to use to let our Oakland County Board of Commissioners know that ICE is breaking the law and making our nation unsafe and that we expect them to take every action available to protect our residents and public servants and ensure that all of us can access government services without fear of violence or intimidation.

Click [here](https://www.mobilize.us/neoaklandindivisible/event/904920/) to sign up to attend the next BOC meeting and to give or witness public testimony. It makes a difference when we show up!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/904903/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
