        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Whistle Making Kit Party</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 8, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Trenton Cultural Center<br>2427 West Rd<br>Trenton, MI 48183</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible: Downriver United 734</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>🗣️📣 LET’S BLOW THE WHISTLE, DOWNRIVER! 📣🗣️
Join Indivisible: Downriver United 734 for a Whistle Kit Making Party and help us build community safety together!

🗓 Sunday, March 8th
⏰ 2–4 PM
📍 Trenton Cultural Center

We’ll be assembling warning whistle kits to distribute throughout the community, a simple, proven way to look out for one another. These kits have been effective in cities like Minneapolis and Chicago, and now it’s time to bring them Downriver.

Come hang out, lend a hand, and help us keep our neighbors safe.
❄️🚨 Let’s blow the whistle on ICE! 🚨❄️

All are welcome, see you there! 💙✊</p>
