        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE Out for Good Rally</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Tuesday, February 24, 2026 at 4:30 PM UTC - 6:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br><br>Oxford, MI 48371</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> NE Oakland Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We love our neighbors! We don&apos;t want secret police in our communities! We reject unwarranted &quot;Let me see your papers&quot; inquiries in the USA! We do not agree to detention in concentration camps. We do not support a jobs program or corporate profits built on torture and neglect. Join us as we rally to assert our civil rights and demand an end to ICE!</p>
