<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>## Sign-Waving: We the People -- NO KINGS!

## Topic: ICE Out! until further notice

**Every Tuesday, 5-6 p.m.** -- Stillwater Pedestrian Plaza (by Valley Bookseller)

_Yes, it will be dark, but there is plenty of street lighting for visibility. It might be cold too. Dress warm. We get extra credit for sign waving in the dark and cold!_

Bring friends, family, your congregation, your curling team, your book club, your knitting group, your backgammon pals. We will provide signs, but we encourage you to bring your own sign on the week&apos;s topic!

**Join the Creative Action Team at a local establishment after the protest at 6 p.m. in downtown Stillwater for &quot;Drink &amp; Think.&quot;** Drink &amp; Think is an opportunity to enjoy great conversation, wind down, build community, and share some new creative resistance ideas.</p>
