        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Signs of Solidarity</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 3:30 PM UTC - 6:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Nashville<br><br>Nashville, TN 37206</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible Nashville</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>The Trump administration is sending ICE deep into communities to spread fear among immigrants. Many families—including citizens—are now afraid to go to work, shop, or go about daily life. To show immigrants they are welcome and essential to our communities, we are going to local businesses and asking them to Post signs supporting immigrant neighbors and rejecting ICE intimidation and Create private employee-only spaces that ICE cannot legally enter without a signed judicial warrant.

