    <Placemark>
        <name>ONE PEOPLE&apos;s No Kings 3 United Pushback</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ONE PEOPLE&apos;s No Kings 3 United Pushback</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 6:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Summit Square Shopping Ctr<br>1717 Langhorne Newtown Rd<br>Langhorne, PA 19047</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> ONE PEOPLE</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Last year, in thousands of towns and cities across the country, millions poured into the streets for the largest single-day protest in US history. 

On March 28 we&apos;ll take to the streets again, ready to bring millions of new allies along with us to declare, in one voice: NO thugs terrorizing our neighborhoods. NO troop deployments in our streets. NO imperial wars of conquest. NO KINGS.

Trump clearly wishes to rule like a king. But -- as every community targeted by ICE and CBP has shown -- we the people refuse to cower in the face of his cruelty. This country doesn&apos;t bow down to tyrants. We sure as hell won&apos;t bow down to the kinds of wretched ghouls who kidnap children, teargas schools, and murder our neighbors then slander them as domestic terrorists.

This regime’s ongoing brutality and authoritarianism have only convinced more Americans, including many who’ve never attended a protest in their lives, to join their neighbors in the streets. Now we&apos;ve got to keep that momentum growing, with the same creativity and dogged determination.

Everything we&apos;ve done so far is the stuff of history. And together, we&apos;ll write the history of how, for the second time in 250 years, we the people defied, and overcame, a tyrant.

Once again ONE PEOPLE will do our part to fight against an Autocratic President and to Safeguard Our Democracy!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/893440/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
