        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE OUT Protest: Hosted by Kyle Little (Congressional Candidate: NJ-12)</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, February 22, 2026 at 8:00 PM UTC - 9:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Monument Square Park<br>2 Livingston Ave<br>New Brunswick, NJ 08901</p>
