<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This protest is about rallying our community and demanding that ICE be removed from our neighborhoods. ICE has been terrorizing our families, targeting immigrants, and spreading fear in our communities for far too long. We will not stay silent. It’s time to stand together and demand justice ICE must be abolished.
Come with your signs and get ready to join the fight!</p>
