        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Albany Day of Action : Tax the Rich, Stop Helping ICE, Public Power Now!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Tuesday, March 10, 2026 at 1:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>12224<br><br>Albany, NY 12224</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> For The Many</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us in Albany for a huge day of action on Tuesday, March 10th to call on state legislators to do the right thing: Tax the rich! Stop helping ICE! Pass public power now!

We will have bus stops in Newburgh, Poughkeepsie, and Kingston.

We&apos;ll be joined by organizations from across the state to show our power—because organized people beat organized money every time. Invite a friend or neighbor and come be a part of the action!</p>
