        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Chelsea Neighbors United - ICE Out of Hudson River Park!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 6:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Chelsea Piers<br>West 22nd Street entrance, near the big blue Chelsea Piers sign.<br>New York, NY 10011</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Hands Off NYC</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>The Hudson River Park Trust has ignored the over 2,900 letters that CNU folks have sent as well as our elected leaders&apos; call to end the ICE contract with them which allows ICE cars to park at Pier 40. We are going to Chelsea Piers to demand ICE OUT OF OUR PARKS NOW!
This is part of Hands Off NYC Weekend of Action! Come join us for joyful resistance, meet your neighbors, and help us grow our movement.</p>
