<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>645 10th Ave<br>New York, NY 10036</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Hands Off NYC</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us for a Day of Action with Hands Off NYC and the Hell’s Kitchen Community Cupboard! Let’s protect our community from ICE by educating our neighbors on their rights, distributing rapid response resources, and building a culture of care and resistance right here in Hell’s Kitchen.</p>
