<h3>Hands Off NYC Neighborhood Action: Protest at a Target store in Manhattan Valley</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, February 22, 2026 at 9:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Target<br>795 Columbus Ave<br>New York, NY 10025</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Hands Off NYC</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>For Neighborhood Weekend of Action join Upper West Side Action Group to protest Target&apos;s complicity/cooperation with ICE. We&apos;ll be singing protest song outside, walking inside store wearing t-shirts with our message on them, purchasing then returning to waste their time, handout informational leaflets outside and deliver a letter to the target manager with our demands. There zoom orientation on Friday, February 20 at 6pm. The zoom link will be sent out to everyone who signs up on Friday morning. We&apos;ll all be meeting in front of the Target store at 4pm on Sunday, Feb 22.</p>
