<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join Upper West Side Action Group to protest Target&apos;s complicity/cooperation with ICE. We&apos;ll be singing protest song outside, walking inside store wearing t-shirts with our message on them,  handout informational leaflets outside and deliver a letter to the target manager with our demands.  There zoom orientation on Friday, February 20 at 6pm.  The zoom link will be sent out to everyone who signs up on Friday morning.
