<h3>Small Business ICE Preparation Training</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, February 22, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>City Tabernacle of Seventh-day Adventists<br>562 W 150th St<br>New York, NY 10031</p>
