        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Petitioning with Antonio Reynoso‼️</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Tuesday, February 24, 2026 at 12:30 PM UTC - 2:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>New York&apos;s 7th Congressional District<br><br>New York, NY 11222</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Reynoso for Congress</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us for the first week of petitioning with Antonio Reynoso! We will be gathering signatures at various locations throughout the week to get Antonio on the ballot this June 23rd.

Let&apos;s speak to voters about taxing the rich, abolishing ICE, and fighting for healthcare and housing for all!

No experience? No problem. We do a training before each and every petitioning session, and you can always be paired up with a veteran petitioner!

Once you sign up for a time slot, locations will be sent to you.</p>
