        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Target Boycott Community Outreach</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Target<br>1598 Flatbush Ave<br>Brooklyn, NY 11210</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Hands Off NYC</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join NYC&apos;s Resistance against ICE &amp; Target! Help us grow the Target Boycott by sharing flyers with shoppers in Flatbush and distributing whistle kits with some chanting &amp; singing to keep it joyful! We will gather outside, with the possibility of an optional indoor action.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/904107/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
