        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>WARM HEARTS MELT ICE!!- PEACEFUL PROTEST RALLY</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 4:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Litchfield Town Green<br>46 West St<br>Litchfield, CT 06759</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> The Northwest Resistance</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>WE MUST STAND TOGETHER AND KEEP RESISTING IN 2026! Bring your energy and your signs, non-violent and PG-13 PLEASE,  and join the Northwest Resistance in speaking out &amp; standing up against this authoritarian regime! Every 2nd &amp; 4th Saturday through winter, on the Litchfield Town Green.  11am - 12pm

Pick the issue you are the most passionate about and bring your sign, PG-13 &amp; non-violent PLEASE. This is a 5 alarm fire and we need everyone to STAND UP, SPEAK OUT AND RESIST!!

We commit to non-violent protest, and do not engage, taunt, speak to or make obscene gestures to or at counter protesters.  Best to smile, ignore, turn your back to them, wish them the day they deserve or drown them out with kazooing, cowbells or a noisemaker.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/879783/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
