<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Together, Long Island</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We&apos;re getting together on Saturday, Feb 21st for the first in a series, where we&apos;ll welcome candidates for a 1 on 1 conversation about their vision and plans for our country and our area.  As always, we&apos;ll gather to build community, share information about the upcoming primary elections, important events and actions, and strategize about the way forward. We&apos;re also very excited to welcome Ahmad Perez of Islip Forward for an important update on ICE activity in our local communities.</p>
