        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>UNITE AND RESIST KEENE</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 5:00 PM UTC - 6:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>23 Central Square<br>Keene, NH 03431</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Weekly Unite and Resist Rally

Join us as we STAND UP for DEMOCRATIC VALUES.

Join us as we STAND UP FOR MORAL DECENCY.

Join us as we STAND AGAINST ICE and the terror, violence, and murders perpetrated by this administration.

Bring your signs. Bring your Flags.
Bring your enthusiasm, acoustic instruments, bells, and chimes.
Bring handouts to share information about groups/actions/networks you are involved in. 


We are stronger together!



A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. 

We ask that you do not engage with agitators or counter-protestors.

We ask all participants to strive to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values or seek assistance from a Peace Keeper (wearing a white safety vest).</p>
