        <name>ICE OUT</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE OUT</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>2730 W University Dr<br>Denton, TX 76201</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This a local Indivisible event!

Come out and help us make noise and get noticed for not only Minnesota but for Maine, Arizona, and of course Texas! Ice is spreading across the country and we need to make sure they know they are not welcome here! 

This is a peaceful protest in the razor ranch area on the corners of Town Center trail and University in the Rayzor Ranch  area, in front of the first United Bank, Denton.

We will be on the North north east corner and hopefully have people that spread down both sides of the street. This is a high visibility area with a lot of traffic. Come out and help us make noise and bring awareness to people of what&apos;s going on in the country right now.. 

There is lots of parking in the shopping areas around this intersection, so please make sure that you patronize one or more of these businesses and let them know that they matter to us.

*A core principle behind all Indivisible events is a commitment to nonviolent action. We expect all participants to seek to de-escalate any potential confrontation with those who disagree with our values.*</p>
