        <name>Carrollton Democrats - Nico Nights with Neighbors</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Carrollton Democrats - Nico Nights with Neighbors</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, February 19, 2026 at 12:30 AM UTC - 2:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Nico&apos;s Cocina - Event Room (to right of restaurant)<br>3065 N Josey Ln, Ste 24<br>Carrollton, TX 75007</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Denton County Democratic Party</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Please join us for our once a month (third Wednesday) meeting of the Carrollton Democrats. Learn why LOCAL ELECTIONS MATTER this January and February as part of a TWO PART SERIES. 

PLEASE NOTE - This meeting we are asking folks to come early if they can to participate in #CRAFTIVISM. If you arrive at 5 or later - we will be creating Whistle ICE 🧊 KITS to be distributed at the NoKings 3.0 event March 28th. The Meeting and Presentation will begin a little before 7pm. 

The February 18th evening&apos;s program is Part Two of all about Local Government and Local Elections with a presentation by Adam Polter with a panel of current and former public officials. Come learn about Carrollton City Government, CFBISD, local election turnout trends, highlight issues important to you, participate in interactive online polls, and much more. This will be a very exciting and informative evening and we hope to see you there. 

WELCOME to the Carrollton Democrats Club. Our focus is to get to know our Neighbors - to meet like-minded folks for fellowship, education, solidarity and purpose.  Learn how WE can shape our plans as we seek to SAVE OUR COUNTRY AND DEMOCRACY!  

We are a Grass Roots Group dedicated to preserving our American way of Life that honors the Individual with Diversity, Equality and Dignity. Learn about ways you can participate in ACTIVISM.  Learn how you may participate in our HIVES (Precinct) project.  We are Creating FUN Caring Communities - and Winning Elections!  And we are building on our momentum from 2025 thanks to your growing enthusiasm! 

Let us help you find ways that you may use your skills, talents and strengths to participate in our fight to take back our country thru activism, demonstrations, precinct building, voter registration and much more.  

Our Goal is to be a source of Information to all Carrollton Democrats so they may make informed and wise decisions at the voting booth. 

We now have a Web Site: https://www.carrolltondemocrats.com/. This will provide our Carrollton Democrats the resources they need whether they live in Denton or Dallas County.  

JOIN US every 3rd Wednesday of the Month:
Nico Nights with the Neighbors - Nico&apos;s Cocina (6:30 to 8:30). 

3065 N. Josey Lane, Carrollton, TX 75007

We meet in the EVENT ROOM to the right of the restaurant. 

Please sign up on Mobilize so we may prepare enough materials for everyone. 

If you wish to be placed on our email list, (only 3-4 a month) please SIGN UP on CarrolltonDemocrats.com.  And we&apos;ll be able to introduce you to your neighbors in your precinct.   

Again - we are happy you have found us - look forward to meeting you!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/799017/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
