        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NO KINGS 3 ARLINGTON TX</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 3:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>700 E Abram St<br>Arlington, TX 76010</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Progressive Women of Arlington TX</p>
