<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join the Newburyport Democratic City Committee and a growing group of concerned citizens for a peaceful weekly standout at the Bartlet Mall in Newburyport, every Saturday from 11 AM - 12 PM. Sign up here for dates through this month.

