        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>BI - Drop Your ICE Contracts</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 28, 2026 at 9:00 PM UTC - 10:30 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>BI Corporate Headquarters<br>6265 Gunbarrel Ave Suite B<br>Boulder, CO 80301</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> SoBoCo Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>In 2025, ICE paid BI Incorporated over $171.5 million for their electronic monitoring or “e-carceration” tools. That includes a secretive $1.6 million
contract for a bounty hunter-like service called “skip tracing”, where BI Incorporated tracks the locations of immigrants in their communities for ICE ERO. They are currently owned by GEO which is a private prison company that runs the Aurora Concentration Camp for detainees.

Join us outside BI&apos;s Boulder County offices to let them know we do not want businesses here that support ICE! We demand BI drop those contracts!!!</p>
