        <name>Dems and Friends Thursday Ice House Crawl</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Dems and Friends Thursday Ice House Crawl</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, February 27, 2026 at 12:00 AM UTC - 2:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Breakaway Brewing<br>1518 E Grayson St<br>San Antonio, TX 78208</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Bexar County Democrats</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Every Thursday, 6-8 PM, we go to a different place with a laid back vibe just to schmooze and find out who&apos;s who. We also discover ice houses and other neighborhood watering holes that tell us a story about San Antonio history and culture.

Our motto, like the American Revolutionaries is &quot;Join or Die!&quot; because together we can do anything and separately, we can do nothing. And we think the best way to join is by having fun. A laid back vibe and good beer, interesting casual conversation, some good food, and VOILA! Fun and friends! 

The Crawls and the Dems are going to be bigger, better and bolder right here, right now. So we&apos;re looking for new friends to join the old. Bring someone with you, meet someone new as well as getting together with old friends for a good mix and mingle. If you&apos;re curious about what Democrats are about, this is a good way to learn about them in a natural habitat.

This is a low expectation event--no hard start or stop time--come and go when you feel like it--no sitting in one spot, no listening to speakers, no pressure to volunteer, not even talking about politics unless you want to.  All you have to do is say hi to someone you don&apos;t know and be nice.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/902015/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
