        <name>PALM BEACH INDIVISIBLES (PBC): &quot;NO KINGS&quot;</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>PALM BEACH INDIVISIBLES (PBC): &quot;NO KINGS&quot;</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, March 28, 2026 at 3:00 PM UTC - 5:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Target - Palm Beach Lakes, Blvd. WPB<br>1760 Palm Beach Lakes Blvd<br>West Palm Beach, FL 33401</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Palm Beach Indivisibles</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>NO KINGS - NO THRONES - NO CROWNS


Palm Beach Indivisibles is organizing another powerful Palm Beach County “NO KINGS” protest on Saturday, March 28, 2026, from 11:00 a.m. to 1:00 p.m. The moment is now, and the stakes could not be higher.

Our last NO KINGS action brought nearly 4,000 people to the front lines of one of the most heavily traveled corridors in the county, commanding the attention of thousands of residents and U.S. and international visitors alike. This time, we’re going even bigger.

Crowds of 6,000 or more are expected to flood the streets in a united stand to Fight Fascism, Defend Democracy, and demand a country that works for all of us—not just the billionaire class. We will raise our voices against ICE abuses, the crushing cost of living, and the rise of millionaire and billionaire oligarchs who believe power belongs to them alone.

This is not a spectator moment. History is written by those who show up. Bring your signs. Bring your neighbors. Bring your outrage and your hope. If you’ve ever said, “enough is enough,” this is where you turn words into action.

No kings. No oligarchs. No silence.
March with us. Show up. Be counted.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/894851/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
