<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>I-17 and Carefree Highway<br><br>Phoenix, AZ 85085</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> LD3 Democrats</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We Stand with Our Neighbors.
We refuse to look away. 

Join your local Democrats on Saturday, February 28, 2026, from 11:00 AM to 1:00 PM as we gather on the Carefree Highway overpass to stand in solidarity with our immigrant neighbors and raise our collective voice against the abuses carried out by ICE. When we show up together, we send a clear message: our neighbors deserve protection, not persecution.

