        <name>Issaquah 98027 and 98029: Adopt a Corner</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Issaquah 98027 and 98029: Adopt a Corner</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, October 8, 2025 at 7:00 AM UTC - 7:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> National Day Laborer Organizing Network</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Have you seen ICE abuses and wanted to nonviolently act in the face of this brutality and injustice? We are calling on all allies in or around the 98027 and the 98029 zip code to Adopt a Day Labor Corner in your neighborhood. Day laborers are our neighbors most vulnerable to harassment and arrest. Let&apos;s show up for them. Be present. Be consistent. Build relationships and offer protection.

A volunteer organizer will contact you once signed up.

Thanks!</p>
