Jamie will discuss what history has taught her about community organizing and creating long-lasting resistance. She is a Summa Cum Laude graduate of Cal State Fullerton who earned a BA in history and a Master&apos;s degree in American Studies. While she was a student she worked as a political organizer and for the Bernie Sanders campaign.

