<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Southcenter Pkwy &amp; Minkler Blvd (outside IHOP)<br>17250 Southcenter Pkwy, Tukwila, WA 98188<br>Tukwila, WA 98188</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Southend Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join Southend Indivisible to rally for democracy and freedom, and against ICE terror and the fascist, un-American Trump regime.  At our rallies we hear thousands of honks and cheers from cars and people passing by, make new friends, play music, and have fun!

