        <name>JUSTICE FOR GOOD. ABOLISH ICE: Lynnwood</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>JUSTICE FOR GOOD. ABOLISH ICE: Lynnwood</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 8:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Tesla Lynnwood<br>17731 Pacific Hwy<br>Lynnwood, WA 98037</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Seattle Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Renee Good deserves justice and we won&apos;t stand silently while her murder is covered up. Join our protest in honor of Renee and in solidarity with immigrant communities across the United States. 

**Trump&apos;s devastating cuts to Medicare and other critical programs so he can give massive tax breaks to billionaires are unconscionable.**Join us in protesting the attack on our rights, the plundering of our country, **and the billionaire who made it all possible.**

Our protests have helped force Musk from DC but our work is far from done. Tesla&apos;s stock is UP because investors think we&apos;re going to fade away. That&apos;s not going to happen.

**Without Musk&apos;s backing, Trump wouldn&apos;t be president and we wouldn&apos;t have to fear for the future of our country. Our democracy has never faced someone with so much money and so little shame as Elon Musk and he&apos;ll remain a danger until we take Tesla&apos;s stock to single digits.**

Please, join us. We need your voice. Let&apos;s make some noise!

See you Saturday!

— Devin

The local #TeslaTakedown crew including Defund Musk, Troublemakers, and Seattle Indivisible work in partnership to organize events throughout the Seattle Metro area.

Tesla Takedown is a peaceful protest movement. We oppose violence, vandalism, and destruction of property. Please treat Tesla drivers with respect as they are most likely on our side!

#TeslaTakedown #BoycottTesla #DefundMusk</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/829120/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
