        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>2/22 Organizing Training Series: Basebuilding</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, February 22, 2026 at 9:00 PM UTC - 12:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>El Centro de la Raza<br>2524 16th Avenue South, Seattle WA 98144<br>Seattle 98144</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Washington Working Families Party</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join the Seattle WFP as we share what we have learned as a group that focuses on skill-building, community-building, and political education work that increases our power to elect leaders who stand up for working people.  Learn how we can work together to organize and grow community in Seattle to achieve our goals: affordable housing for all, universal childcare, ICE out of Washington, and much more.

Join us as we share how we organize through one-on-one community building and the use of digital tools. We are excited to see you there!</p>
