        <name>NE Tacoma Community Safety Meeting</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>NE Tacoma Community Safety Meeting</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Tuesday, February 24, 2026 at 2:00 AM UTC - 3:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Browns Point United Methodist Church<br>5339 Browns Point Blvd NE<br>Tacoma, WA 98422</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> National Day Laborer Organizing Network</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>NE Tacoma educators and community members are organizing an Adopt-a-School group to strengthen our community connections and protect our students and families from ICE. This is our first meeting to start planning logistics and scheduling shifts.</p>
