        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE OUT! JUSTICE FOR ICE VICTIMS: Tacoma</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 8:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Union Station - Federal Courthouse<br>1717 Pacific Ave<br>Tacoma, WA 98402</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Seattle Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>**THEY WANT US SILENT. WE&apos;RE DEFIANT.**
Keith Porter, Renee Good, Alex Pretti, and other victims of ICE deserve justice. Join our protest in solidarity with Minnesota and immigrant communities across the United States as **we continue to oppose Trump and the billionaires who made this fascist regime possible.**

We need your voice. Let&apos;s make some noise!

See you Saturday!

— Devin

PS. For the full schedule of events, see DefundMusk.com/events

The local #TeslaTakedown crew including Defund Musk, Troublemakers, and Seattle Indivisible work in partnership to organize events throughout the Seattle Metro area.

This is a peaceful protest movement. We oppose violence, vandalism, and destruction of property.</p>
