<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> NELA Alliance for Democracy</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We look forward to seeing you at our next in-person meeting to connect, inform, and inspire. We will be amping up for the year&apos;s actions and campaigns, and will have many ways you can each become involved and make a difference.

