        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Whistlemania! LBC: Neighborhood Folding Event at Sports Basement</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, February 27, 2026 at 1:30 AM UTC - 3:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Sports Basement Long Beach<br>2100 N Bellflower Blvd<br>Long Beach, CA 90815</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Long Beach Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This event in the community space upstairs at Sports Basement, check with the front desk or follow signs to find us. 

Fold zines, make whistle packs with us, and learn about how to become more involved in the opposition.

We saw the reports of Chicago residents coming together with indignant spirit and whistles around their necks to care for their neighbors and KICK ICE OUT. Following that lead, our Whistlemania! LBC goal is to put 16,000 whistle packs into the hands of Long Beach residents during the next 3 months as a sign of dissent and solidarity.

YOU CAN HELP.

No time to sit and fold? This is also a great time to pick up whistle packs for you and your co-workers, your social club or your extended family (while supplies last). https://linktr.ee/whistlemanialbc

