        <name>CIVIC SUNDAYS + BOYCOTT HOME DEPOT COALITION  ICE BREAKER -SHOW UP, DO SOMETHING - IN PERSON!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>CIVIC SUNDAYS + BOYCOTT HOME DEPOT COALITION  ICE BREAKER -SHOW UP, DO SOMETHING - IN PERSON!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, February 22, 2026 at 11:00 PM UTC - 1:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br><br>Los Angeles, CA 90028</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Civic Sundays</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Civic Sundays, in conjunction with Boycott Home Depot Coalition is planning an BOYCOTT HOME DEPOT ABOLISH ICE action at Home Depot the weekend of Feb 22, and we need your participation!  

L.A. is a car culture, and we hope to use that against them.  Unlike most, the Home Depot we&apos;re highlighting has limited parking, and, with your help, WE are going to fill their parking lots!  

Once we have accomplished that, we&apos;ll be picketing the parking lot entrances, entering the store to buy &amp; return Ice Scrapers ($1.08 each).  We will keep paying customers out, and we will jam their cashiers with transactions that make them zero profit.  

Sign up so we know how many cars/people we can count on and coordinate our action!

Thanks for showing up and doing something!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/898752/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
