        <name>ICE Out Whistle Kit Assembly Event</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE Out Whistle Kit Assembly Event</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, March 4, 2026 at 2:00 AM UTC - 4:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Torrance Municipal Airport - Zamperini Field<br>3301 Airport Dr<br>Torrance, CA 90505</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible South Bay LA</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>ICE and CBP are terrorizing neighborhoods around the country. The key to disrupting their operations is to Get Loud and Form A Crowd, and to take lots of videos. Let&apos;s get together and prepare, so that we can help our friends and neighbors when they target the LA area again. 

Please join us in assembling Whistle Kits that we can distribute to attendees at our events. Each kit will include: 
1) 1 whistle for people to use if ICE shows up in their neighborhoods
2) 5 know-your-rights red cards to give to people who might be at risk
3) 2 flyers for businesses to post stating that a judicial warrant is needed for entry and law enforcement operations
4) General instructions on how to use the kit
5) Instructions on the best way to resist ICE operations

We&apos;ll have snacks and light beverages, and discuss some things we can do to get ourselves ready.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/899078/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
