<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Southwest Oleson Road &amp; Southwest Garden Home Road<br>Beaverton, OR 97223</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> SW Indivisible Resistance</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>This is one of 5 corners we will be covering on NO KINGS 3. ICE out of our elections! We are here to make a better world. Let’s line the streets and bring family, friends, signs, flags, noise-makers and banners. Nonviolent, peaceful and fun resistance . The regime are losers on every front – domestically, economically and internationally and an embarrassment to our country.

Join us. THIS IS WHAT DEMOCRACY LOOKS LIKE!

We have timed this so you can leave with enough time to get downtown for the march.  Soon we will post the bus stop close to this intersection and the time it leaves to go down to the waterfront.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/897925/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
