        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Protest with Woodburn Indivisible&apos;s Geezers for Good Saturdays! Come to a Meeting Too!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 8:00 PM UTC - 10:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>2900 Tom Tennant Dr<br>Woodburn, OR 97071</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Woodburn Hubbard Aurora Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join the Woodburn Hubbard Aurora Indivisible&apos;s Geezers for Good weekly rallies at the Woodburn Transit Center on Hwy 214, just east of I-5. We&apos;re there every Saturday from 12 to 2 PM. Contact us at WoodburnIndivisible@Yahoo.com. We also have weekly meetings so email us about joining. Become part of our family of dedicated protesters who show up in any weather to protest, them meet weekly to plan. If you&apos;ve been thinking you should do more to fight back against the ICE kidnappings, assaults, shootings, tyranny and hate, join us this Saturday. On the picket line, you&apos;ll see the best of humanity, caring people who brave the cold, wind and rain to demand change. If you&apos;ve been feeling sad or angry, this is your antidote. By the time you put away your sign at 2 PM, feelings of sadness and fear will be replaced with a sense of accomplishment and shared purpose. Join our powerhouse community of determined, unstoppable protesters.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/892375/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
