        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>It&apos;s Blue Turn Casual Coffee Social</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Sunday, March 1, 2026 at 9:30 PM UTC - 11:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Panera Bread<br>20807 Stevens Creek Blvd<br>Cupertino, CA 95014</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> It&apos;s Blue Turn</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us for a relaxed community coffee chat in Cupertino: an informal space to meet other group members, ask questions, share ideas, and connect. Brand new? Have been with us for a while? Just a curious non-member? Come on by!

**We&apos;ll talk about No Kings 3, protecting our community against ICE terror, winning elections in 2026, and anything else you&apos;d like to discuss.**

**What to expect:**  
- Friendly faces and casual conversation  
- Brief updates on upcoming campaigns and actions
- A chance to share what’s working and how we can all save our country

Please RSVP so we know how many muffins to get! :)

Next monthly organizing meeting is https://www.mobilize.us/indivisible/event/750621/</p>
