<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Indivisible</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join us at 31st and El Camino at Hillsdale Mall in front of West Elm Furniture store in San Mateo to exercise our 1st Amendment rights to protest the lawless, unaccountable behavior of the Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE) agents who are terrorizing American communities across the country. 

