    <Placemark>
        <name>Join the OC Indivisible Coalition</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Join the OC Indivisible Coalition</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, September 18, 2025 at 7:00 AM UTC - 8:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> OC Indivisible Coalition</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>## WE&apos;RE FIGHTING BACK AGAINST AUTHORITARIANISM IN ORANGE COUNTY ##

### JOIN OTHERS IN YOUR AREA ###

**City Groups** are forming throughout Orange County. Each group does some or all of the following: hold regular weekly rallies; collect food and essential items for mutual aid; hold weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly meetings as a group; go to their city council, school board, and water board meetings; strategize with our community partners on how best to respond to this moment in history and support their neighborhoods. 

Please sign up with a valid email address and accurate zip code, and we will help you connect with your local group. Check the box if you&apos;re willing to help lead or host a team in your area! 

*(meetings and events can be hosted in public locations; hosts help with set-up and greet attendees.)*

### FIGHTING FOR DEMOCRACY, TOGETHER ###

**Help us grow the resistance locally and build for a better future**

We are pro-democracy, anti-fascism. We work to uphold the Constitution, defeat the Trump agenda, and elect &amp; influence local, state, &amp; federal leaders who reflect their constituents&apos; values. Our goal: transform Orange County into a place where everyone can be safe &amp; truly thrive.

**Our priorities for 2026:**

- Connecting members with like-minded neighbors to build community

- Growing our volunteer base for ICE Watch, community care &amp; mutual aid in our local areas

- Holding our locally elected public servants accountable &amp; advocating for progressive policies

- Education and outreach with voters for progressive wins in local elections

### ABOUT THE OC INDIVISIBLE COALITION ###

**[The OC Indivisible Coalition](https://linktr.ee/ocindivisiblecoalition)** is a collaboration between the **[Indivisible](https://indivisible.org/)** groups in and touching Orange County, CA. We are non-partisan, all-volunteer, grassroots groups of residents in OC who are fighting fascism and holding elected officials accountable, from city councils and school boards all the way up to Congress. We partner with other community organizations to uplift and support our neighbors while we work toward progressive electoral change and a democracy that works for ALL people.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/846818/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
