        <name>Take Action Now To Save Lives From ICE</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Take Action Now To Save Lives From ICE</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, January 24, 2026 at 5:00 AM UTC - 5:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> MoveOn</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Alex Jeffrey Pretti, Renee Nicole Good, Keith Porter, and many, many others have now been executed by President Trump’s ICE. The administration is murdering people in the streets for peacefully protesting to protect their neighbors and children. It’s heartbreaking and horrifying. Yet in the face of ICE’s brutality, Minnesotans aren’t giving up, they’re showing up. 

In freezing temperatures, tens of thousands of Minnesotans are taking the streets, delivering groceries to immigrant families, and joining together in community. Minnesota is leading the way, and MoveOn is coming together to stand with them.

Sign the pledge to take action against ICE, and be in solidarity with Minnesotans, and we&apos;ll be in touch with next steps.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/891605/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
