        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Tell JLL not to lease office space to ICE in Carmel</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Wednesday, February 18, 2026 at 5:00 AM UTC - 4:59 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
