<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>As reported by Wired, ICE is expanding to a new office space in Carmel, IN. (https://tinyurl.com/5f92jcyu).  

They have leased (or will be leasing) office space at the Penn on Parkway office park. 

Tell the Carmel City Council that we won&apos;t stand for a larger ICE presence in our community!</p>
