<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We&apos;re calling voters to let them know about the importance of CA-48 to changing Congress and we&apos;re letting them know about Abel&apos;s bold economic agenda to bring immediate change to every American.  All you need is a phone, we&apos;ll provide training.

