        <name>GOTV for Georgia CD14 Special Election and Wisconsin Supreme Court Race</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>GOTV for Georgia CD14 Special Election and Wisconsin Supreme Court Race</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Thursday, February 19, 2026 at 11:00 PM UTC - 1:00 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Engage Blue</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>We&apos;ll be calling/texting South Asian voters in Georgia&apos;s Congressional District 14 to get out the vote for the special election that will be held on March 10th, 2026. This is the house seat that was recently vacated by Marjorie Taylor Greene. As we have seen massive overperformances by Democratic candidate in special elections, there is a possibility that the Democrat can win in this race. However, we are also interested in getting people who live in Georgia in the habit of voting to ensure that Jon Ossoff wins his Senate race this November. 

Additionally, we will also be getting out the vote for the Wisconsin Supreme Court race on April 7th. Here, liberal judge, Chris Taylor, will be facing off against Maria Lazer, a conservative judge. This election for this open race could expand the liberal majority on the Wisconsin state Supreme Court.

Thirdly, we will be calling voters living in states represented by moderate Republicans to encourage them to contact their Senators in support of the changes to ICE&apos;s behaviors requested by Democrats in order to fund the Department of Homeland Security. These changes include forcing ICE to seek warrants before detaining people and requiring that ICE officers be unmasked.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/906232/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
