    <Placemark>
        <name>ICE OUT! Text Bank &amp; Listening Party 📲✊🏽🪩</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>ICE OUT! Text Bank &amp; Listening Party 📲✊🏽🪩</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, February 20, 2026 at 12:00 AM UTC - 1:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> United We Dream Action</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>From the streets of LA and Minneapolis to the Grammy stage, the message is clear: **ICE has no place in our communities**.

This year, we have witnessed the terror that federal agents are bringing into our community. We&apos;re outraged by the detention of children like five-year old Liam Conejo Ramos and the hundreds more held in horrific conditions - all paid for by OUR tax dollars.

Workers, neighbors, students, immigrants, and allies are all standing together to demand accountability and policies that strengthen our communities. We&apos;re answering hate with love and we&apos;re keeping each other safe.

🔥🧊The Melt ICE Act, introduced by Congresswoman Delia Ramirez, offers a real solution for this moment. This bill prevents DHS from entering new detention contracts and ends all existing immigration detention contracts,  demanding that money is invested back into our communities, where it belongs. 

📲✊ We’re inviting you to **join The Squad on our “ICE OUT Text bank &amp; Listening Party” on Wednesday, February 19th.** Together, we’ll text thousands of UWDA supporters nationwide to urge their representatives to support the MELT ICE Act!

We&apos;ll keep the energy high with a playlist from artists who have declared ICE OUT -  Bad Bunny, Cardi B, Green Day, Kehlani, Billie Eilish, Chappell Roan, SZA, and more! - Join us for action and good vibes! 🕺

P.S. Never text banked before with the Squad? No problem! We’ll be providing training during the session. All you need is a laptop or tablet!</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/900178/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
