<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join the upcoming ACLU MA Action Team briefing to get the latest information about what&apos;s happening at the State House and on-the-ground related to immigration and ICE in Massachusetts. 

You&apos;ll hear from ACLU immigration experts working on state and local policy and in communities throughout the state, and learn ways that you can take action.</p>
