    <Placemark>
        <name>National Call: Defending the 14th &amp; Abolishing ICE!</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>National Call: Defending the 14th &amp; Abolishing ICE!</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Friday, February 20, 2026 at 12:00 AM UTC - 1:30 AM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Popular Democracy</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>#### Join our National Fight Back Call. **We&apos;re organizing to defend the 14th Amendment by abolishing ICE!**

It’s Black History Month, and we are grounding ourselves in truth: America only became a democracy because Black people and our allies defeated chattel slavery. Out of that victory, we won the 14th Amendment which promises citizenship by birth and guarantees that the law must protect us all equally.   

But today, the Trump regime is using ICE to attack the due process our ancestors fought for and to strip away our fundamental freedoms. **We’ve seen this before, and we know that we only keep the rights we are willing to defend.**


**On the call, we will learn:**

* From organizers in Minnesota about the frontline struggle against ICE
* Why we must Abolish ICE to save our 14th Amendment rights
* And how to become a Defender of the 14th!

See you soon!</p>
