<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> AZ LD7 Democrats</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>Join Democrats and Democratic-Leanining Independents from all over our big sprawling Arizona Legislative District 7 for camaraderie, political discussion, and planning.

Beginning at 5:30 pm, we host an ice-breaker for new and returning guests, along with an informal volunteer workshop.

Our regular monthly LD7 Committee meeting begins at 6:00 pm. We typically include presentations from one or more candidates or policy experts on our meeting agenda, along with regular business matters and orientation and training workshops.

