        <name>🚨End ICE, End Billionaires: Our Plan for Mass Strikes 🚨</name>
        <description><![CDATA[
<h3>🚨End ICE, End Billionaires: Our Plan for Mass Strikes 🚨</h3>
<p><strong>When:</strong> Saturday, February 21, 2026 at 6:00 PM UTC - 7:00 PM</p>
<p><strong>Where:</strong><br>Location not specified</p>
<p><strong>Organized by:</strong> Sunrise Movement</p>
<p><strong>About:</strong></p><p>🚨 End ICE, End Billionaires: Our Plan for Mass Strikes! 🚨

Authoritarianism is rising, ICE is terrorizing communities, and Trump and his billionaires are fucking over working people so they can get rich—but we have the power to fight back. Join this 1-hour Sunrise training to learn why noncooperation is our most powerful tool, how to disrupt ICE, and take action toward our May 1st Mass strikes. Leave ready to take action, build community,  and start building the power to rewrite the rules of a system rigged against us. 

About Sunrise Movement: We are a youth-led movement fighting to stop the climate crisis and force the government to invest in Black, brown, and working-class communities. All are welcome, but young people lead our spaces. Learn more and join at smvmt.org/membership (under 35) or smvmt.org/supporter2025 (35+).</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mobilize.us/event/354486/" target="_blank">View Event on Mobilize.us</a></p>
<p><i>Data source: mobilize.us | Updated: 2026-02-18T07:03:09.039Z</i></p>
]]></description>
